comment: R-Slash shows that Mirotic (CHI) brings his right arm down and makes contact with Duncan's arm prior to blocking the shot attempt.
L-Slash shows that Leonard (SAS) cleanly strips the ball from Mirotic (CHI).
Moore (CHI) grabs and holds Ginobili (SAS) and affects his FOM during the inbounds play.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that the ball was last touched by Mirotic (CHI) was upheld. San Antonio was awarded possession.
Gasol (CHI) cleanly blocks Aldridge's (SAS) layup attempt.
Ginobili (SAS) makes contact with Gasol's (CHI) arm that causes him to lose control of the ball.
Moore (CHI) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Ginobili's (SAS) driving shot attempt. The contact on the play is initiated by Ginobili.
Noah (CHI) grabs Aldridge's (SAS) arm and affects his ability to defend.
Noah (CHI) pushes Aldridge (SAS) into Butler (CHI) causing him to make body contact that affects Butler's layup attempt.
Butler (CHI) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Leonard's (SAS) jump shot attempt.
Rose (CHI) cleanly blocks Parker's (SAS) jump shot attempt.
